## Request Flow (User → WAF → Services)

```
User Browser
  │
  ├── GET /* (SPA routes)  →  WAF (:443) → __PROJECT_NAME__-web (:80)
  ├── GET/POST /api/*      →  WAF (:443) → __PROJECT_NAME__-api (:8000)
  ├── WS /ws/*             →  WAF (:443) → __PROJECT_NAME__-api (:8000)
  └── POST /agent/*        →  WAF (:443) → __PROJECT_NAME__-agent (:8000)
```

WAF FQDN: `<set-after-provision>`

